nodes.text:
This clone naval officer was stationed aboard the Star Destroyer Endurance.
He and clone trooper commander Ponds, along with a number of other officers, tried to land the Endurance on the planet Vanqor after the cruiser was sabotaged by Boba Fett. The clone, along with Ponds and Admiral Kilian survived the Endurance crash on Vanqor. However, he and the others were captured by Fett's band of bounty hunters on the planet's surface. Ponds was executed by Fett's accomplice Aurra Sing, but the officer and Kilian were transported to Florrum. There, he and Kilian were rescued by Jedi Padawan Ahsoka Tano as Bossk was about to kill them.
